OL,3,C'Violent bully' who hid in fridge to
OL,4,Cavoid police jailed for three years
OL,6,FThe moment a "violent bully" from
OL,7,FRochester hid in a fridge in an
OL,8,Fattempt to evade police has been
OL,9,Fcaptured on camera.
OL,11,FPolice bodycam footage shows Dean
OL,12,FFoord arguing with officers as they
OL,13,Fremove him from the white good.
OL,15,FThe 33-year-old was arrested after his
OL,16,Fvictim reported the mental and
OL,17,Fphysical abuse she had endured over
OL,18,Fsix months.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
