PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783691327
OL,3,C'Violent bully' who hid in fridge to
OL,4,Cavoid police jailed for three years
OL,6,FKent Police said Foord controlled her
OL,7,Fsocial media accounts and made her cut
OL,8,Fcontact with friends and family
OL,9,Fmembers. He spent all of her money on
OL,10,Fgambling, drugs, alcohol and scratch
OL,11,Fcards.
OL,13,FShe was not allowed to have a phone
OL,14,Fand, whenever she did, Foord would
OL,15,Fdeliberately damage it. He even forced
OL,16,Fher to sell a phone to pay off his
OL,17,Fdrug debt.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
