OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783691327
OL,3,C'Violent bully' who hid in fridge to
OL,4,Cavoid police jailed for three years
OL,6,FThe force also said the woman was only
OL,7,Fallowed to leave the house when Foord
OL,8,Fpermitted her to. On one occasion, he
OL,9,Flocked her in a room and would only
OL,10,Flet her out after making her bark like
OL,11,Fa dog.
OL,13,FAccording to police, Foord was also
OL,14,Fviolent towards the woman. He filmed
OL,15,Fhimself threatening the victim with a
OL,16,Fknife, saying he was going to kill her.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
