OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783691327
OL,3,C'Violent bully' who hid in fridge to
OL,4,Cavoid police jailed for three years
OL,6,FFoord of Brooker Close, Rochester, was
OL,7,Farrested in December 2025. During a
OL,8,Fsearch, officers found him in
OL,9,Fpossession of cocaine. He was later
OL,10,Fcharged.
OL,12,FFollowing a trial, Foord was found
OL,13,Fguilty of actual bodily harm, criminal
OL,14,Fdamage, threats to kill, common
OL,15,Fassault, controlling and coercive
OL,16,Fbehaviour, and possession of a Class A
OL,17,Fdrug.
OL,19,FHe was jailed for three years at
OL,20,FMaidstone Crown Court on Tuesday (30
OL,21,FJune).
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
