OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783691327
OL,3,C'Violent bully' who hid in fridge to
OL,4,Cavoid police jailed for three years
OL,6,FPolice Constable George Fisher said:
OL,7,F"Foord is a violent bully who used
OL,8,Ffear, violence and intimidation to
OL,9,Fcontrol almost every aspect of the
OL,10,Fvictim's life.
OL,12,F"He tried to hide from officers in a
OL,13,Ffridge, but there are no hiding
OL,14,Fplaces. This shows that we will track
OL,15,Foffenders down and bring them to
OL,16,Fjustice.
OL,18,F"I also commend the victim for the
OL,19,Fcourage she has shown in coming
OL,20,Fforward and helping to secure this
OL,21,Fconviction."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
